    <item>
      <title>1st Cardiff NLP Summer Workshop</title>
      <link>https://cardiffnlp.github.io/post/2022-03-10/</link>
      <pubDate>Thu, 10 Mar 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://cardiffnlp.github.io/post/2022-03-10/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;We are organising a &lt;strong&gt;free&lt;/strong&gt; in-person 2-day Natural Language Processing workshop in Cardiff from &lt;strong&gt;June 30 to July 1&lt;/strong&gt;. We will have invited speakers, tutorials, networking, etc.&lt;/p&gt;
